<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Password Email</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>

<body>
    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-5 pb-1">
        <i class="fas fa-cubes fa-2x me-3" style="color: #4983e2;"></i>
        <h1 class="h1 fw-bold mb-0">ElasticFind</h1>
    </div>

    <h2 class="mb-2 pb-3" style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Reset Your Password</h2>

    <h5 class="mb-2">We received a request to reset your password. If you initiated this request, you can reset your password by clicking the link below:</h5>

    <h5 class="mb-2"><a href="{{resetPasswordLink}}" target="_blank">Reset your password</a></h5>

    <p class="mb-2">If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email. Your current password will remain unchanged.</p>

    <p class="mb-2">This link will expire in 24 hours for your security.</p>

    <p class="mb-2">If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact our support team.</p>

    <p class="mb-2">Thanks,</p>

    <h3>Team ElasticFind</h3>
</body>

</html>